casebody.data:
Kevin DUGAN, Plaintiff-Respondent,
and
Roman Zielonka, Plaintiff,
v.
BEST BUY CO. INC., and Garrett Hetrick, Defendants-Petitioners. C-336 September Term 2017
080016 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 17, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001897-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
